rolls (soundtrack)|Trolls: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Be Yourself\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| ''[[Little (film)|Little]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Wolf at Your Door\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/chloexhalle/status/1118186190866403334|title=wolf at your door\" out 4/26 \ud83d\udc3a\ud83d\udc3a #forthethrone|via=[[Twitter]]|date=April 16, 2019|accessdate=April 17, 2019}}</ref>\n| ''[[Game of Thrones (season 8)|For the Throne]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2019/04/game-of-thrones-soundtrack-for-the-throne|title='Game of Thrones' Soundtrack 'For the Throne' Features the Weeknd, Travis Scott, ASAP Rocky, and More|date=April 9, 2019|accessdate=April 13, 2019|work=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Enchanted\"\n|''[[El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie]]''\n|}\n\n=== Guest appearances ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Title\n!Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Artist(s)\n! scope=\"col\"|Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lonely Road\"\n|2017\n| [[Willow Smith]]\n| ''The 1st''<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/willow-romance|title=Listen to Willow's Introspective Thoughts on \"Romance\" \u2022 EBONY|date=October 27, 2017|work=EBONY|access-date=October 27, 2018|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"[[Silver Bells]]\"\n| 2019\n| [[Dionne Warwick]]\n| ''Dionne Warwick & The Voices of Christmas''\n|}\n\n==Concert tours==\n'''Opening act'''\n* [[Beyonc\u00e9]] \u2013 [[The Formation World Tour]] (2016)\n* [[Andra Day]] \u2013 [[Cheers to the Fall]] Tour (2016)\n* [[Jay-Z]] and [[Beyonc\u00e9]] \u2013 [[On the Run II Tour]] (2018)\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Film !! Chloe !! Halle\n|-\n|2003\n|''[[The Fighting Temptations]]''\n|Young Lilly\n|{{n/a}}\n|-\n|2006\n|''[[Last Holiday (2006 film)|Last Holiday]]''\n|Anna\n|Tina\n|-\n|2008\n|''[[Meet t